      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "Director, FBI",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "text": "RE: DETROIT FLYING SAUCER CLUB",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "ESPIONAGE - X",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "2. Group representation to the Board of Directors",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "of the club.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "The group leaders are supposed to control discussion, and not offend",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "any religious belief.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "At this meeting, [REDACTED] a group leader, [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "Detroit, said that [REDACTED] opposed group meetings",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "because of accusations against them of subversive activities. An",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "unidentified person said he did not think it true, but it was alleged",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "one member of the Board of Directors was a Communist. [REDACTED] answered",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "this by saying he would mention no names, but the accuser should see",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "him about this, and the accused was not a Communist. He said fellow",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "travellers could get in or infiltrate the club, but he was at a loss",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "as to any way of controlling that. As a result of this meeting,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "[REDACTED] felt the group was either subversive, or a new religious group.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "He felt it all stems from ADAMSKI in California. He said one [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "[REDACTED] a flying saucer speaker, had moved to Detroit.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "At this meeting, [REDACTED] said that had saucer landings occurred",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "in Detroit, in October, the group leaders would have been first to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "know it. He said he reported to ADAMSKI the predictions of MARKER",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "and ADAMSKI felt she should not predict more than 30 days in advance,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "and, even that was no good sometimes.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "On November 4, 1954, [REDACTED] said [REDACTED] advised him [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "another addition to his group was [REDACTED] and also, [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "Farmington.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "[REDACTED] said that on November 8, 1954, [REDACTED] advised",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "him she was resigning from the Board of Directors of the Club as she",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "had too many outside interests, and she had to eat. She said she was",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "going to show the film, \"The Day the Earth Stood Still\", around",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "Michigan, as a result of having met two men (not named). She said",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "ADAMSKI, in California, was her God, even admitting his earthly",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "faults.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "status": "blank"
    },
